	<!-- EN: {PAWN_labelShort} has developed ear rot in {PAWN_possessive} {2}, due to not washing {PAWN_possessive} ears regularly and properly.\n\nThe affected ear will slowly lose function over the next {3} days, before dying completely.\n\nThis infection can be slowly treated by repeated tending with medicine, or quickly cured with an Elixir of Harmony. -->
	<Mousekin_Disease_EarRot.letterText>{PAWN_labelShort}因未定期妥善清洗{PAWN_possessive}耳朵，導致其{2}側患上耳腐病。\n\n受感染的耳朵將在未來{3}天內逐漸喪失功能，最終完全壞死。\n\n此感染可透過反覆用藥緩慢治療，或使用白鼠族和諧靈丹快速治癒。</Mousekin_Disease_EarRot.letterText>
	
